<div style="text-align: center;">
EnSelle has generously donated a 54 cm Ridley track frame for an OBRA auction. Send in your bid now! Auction closes June 30, 5:00 PM.
<br>
<br>
Current bid: <%= @highest_bid.name %>, $<%= @highest_bid.amount %>
<br>
Time left: <%= distance_of_time_in_words_to_now(DateTime.new(2007, 7, 1, 11, 0, 0)) %>
<br>
<br>
<%= link_to(image_tag('http://www.airevalleycycles.com/smsimg/34/1801-4273-main-oval-34.jpg', :width => 400, :height => 256), 
            'http://www.airevalleycycles.com/products.php?plid=m4b34s25p1801&tbv=RIDLEY_Oval_Frames_Road/Track/Time_Trial') %>
<br>
<br>

<%= error_messages_for('bid') %>

<%= form_tag :action => 'send_bid' %>
<div align="center">
<table class="base" align="center">
	<tr>
		<td>Name:</td>
		<td><%= text_field 'bid', 'name' %></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td>Email address:</td>
		<td><%= text_field 'bid', 'email' %></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td>Phone number:</td>
		<td><%= text_field 'bid', 'phone' %></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td>Bid amount ($):</td>
		<td><%= text_field 'bid', 'amount', :size => 8 %> <span class="updatedon">Please round bids to whole dollars</span></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2" style="text-align: right;"><%= submit_tag 'Submit Bid' %></td>
	</tr>
</table>
</div>
</form>
</div>